{"tid":2450894,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屯門男子持木棍追打兩青年 反被圍攻扑穿頭","createTime":"2021-03-17T17:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T07:55:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6f4ef1d6fa7c0964f9a86837c9701f256928d9fb","tid":2450894,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"屯門周三（17日）下午發生大混戰，一名身穿花tee的男子手持木棍沿馬路追打兩名青年，其後被青年的朋友趕至圍毆受傷，蜷伏在地上被亂棍施襲近10秒。<br />\n<br />\n下午3時許，讀者劉先生駕駛私家車沿井財街行駛，至金銘大廈附近燈位時，見到兩名青年被一名穿花tee的男子持棍追打，「有一個走咗入隔音屏，好似着校服嘅嗰個就俾個男人捉住喺馬路度打，打到背囊都跌喺地下」。<br />\n<br />\n花tee男眼見青年兩名朋友趕至，意圖跑離現場，惟他突然失足，仆倒在地上，被尾隨跑至的兩人包圍，並持棍狀物瘋狂圍毆，而疑似穿校服的青年坐在路邊休息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210318/LYE7RFM6DBCM7I5BOHFAHBO62Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210318%2FLYE7RFM6DBCM7I5BOHFAHBO62Q%2F&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=48b6aefd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210318%2FLYE7RFM6DBCM7I5BOHFAHBO62Q%2F&h=26a58806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210318/LYE7RFM6DBCM7I5BOHFAHBO62Q/</a>"},{"pid":"c9a9169d8ba6042996e67c93179e53cd4c3081e4","tid":2450894,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283dd60b9fd07ed85c045f28c6ba4bdde160e5d9","tid":2450894,"uid":183844,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:26:06.000Z","msg":"國安大法好"},{"pid":"a17d83296a148f0fe83a97a671d9b4d2d9a70b2d","tid":2450894,"uid":17008,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"紅橋 隔離好多大排擋"},{"pid":"6c4336f6b8e595b9787c2b43413aafa16f76d7ab","tid":2450894,"uid":148017,"like":0,"disli